# UI Component Implementation Guide

rule "ui-components" {
  description = "Implementation patterns for UI components in the Setlify app"
  alwaysApply = true

  ## Reference
  - Full implementation details are documented in `/design/design-system.json`
  - Read this file for exact Tailwind classes and component patterns

  ## Component Library
  - Use shadcn/ui components from `@/components/ui/*`
  - Icon library: lucide-react
  - Styling: Tailwind CSS with CSS variables defined in `src/index.css`
  - Utility: Use `cn()` from `@/lib/utils` for conditional classes

  ## Button Patterns
  ```tsx
  // Primary CTA (use sparingly—one per section)
  <Button>Save Setlist</Button>
  
  // Secondary action
  <Button variant="secondary">Cancel</Button>
  <Button variant="outline">Cancel</Button>
  
  // Destructive
  <Button variant="destructive">Delete</Button>
  
  // Icon button
  <Button variant="ghost" size="icon">
    <PlusIcon className="h-4 w-4" />
  </Button>
  
  // With icon
  <Button><PlusIcon className="mr-2 h-4 w-4" /> Add Song</Button>
  ```

  ## Form Patterns
  ```tsx
  // Labeled input
  <div className="space-y-2">
    <Label htmlFor="name">Name</Label>
    <Input id="name" placeholder="Enter name" />
  </div>
  
  // With helper text
  <div className="space-y-2">
    <Label htmlFor="field">Label</Label>
    <Input id="field" />
    <p className="text-xs text-muted-foreground">Helper text</p>
  </div>
  
  // Form grid
  <div className="grid gap-4">
    {/* fields */}
  </div>
  ```

  ## Card Patterns
  ```tsx
  <Card>
    <CardHeader>
      <CardTitle>Title</CardTitle>
      <CardDescription>Description text</CardDescription>
    </CardHeader>
    <CardContent>
      {/* Content */}
    </CardContent>
    <CardFooter className="justify-end gap-2">
      <Button variant="outline">Cancel</Button>
      <Button>Save</Button>
    </CardFooter>
  </Card>
  ```

  ## Dialog Patterns
  ```tsx
  <Dialog>
    <DialogTrigger asChild>
      <Button>Open</Button>
    </DialogTrigger>
    <DialogContent>
      <DialogHeader>
        <DialogTitle>Title</DialogTitle>
        <DialogDescription>Description</DialogDescription>
      </DialogHeader>
      {/* Content */}
      <DialogFooter>
        <Button variant="outline">Cancel</Button>
        <Button>Confirm</Button>
      </DialogFooter>
    </DialogContent>
  </Dialog>
  ```

  ## Dropdown Menu Pattern
  ```tsx
  <DropdownMenu>
    <DropdownMenuTrigger asChild>
      <Button variant="ghost" size="icon">
        <MoreVerticalIcon className="h-4 w-4" />
      </Button>
    </DropdownMenuTrigger>
    <DropdownMenuContent align="end">
      <DropdownMenuItem>Edit</DropdownMenuItem>
      <DropdownMenuSeparator />
      <DropdownMenuItem className="text-destructive">Delete</DropdownMenuItem>
    </DropdownMenuContent>
  </DropdownMenu>
  ```

  ## List Patterns
  ```tsx
  // Stacked list with dividers
  <div className="divide-y divide-border">
    {items.map((item) => (
      <div key={item.id} className="flex items-center justify-between py-4">
        <div className="space-y-1">
          <p className="font-medium">{item.title}</p>
          <p className="text-sm text-muted-foreground">{item.subtitle}</p>
        </div>
        {/* Actions */}
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>
  
  // Grid of cards
  <div className="grid gap-4 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
    {/* Cards */}
  </div>
  ```

  ## Empty State Pattern
  ```tsx
  <div className="flex flex-col items-center justify-center py-12 text-center">
    <IconName className="h-12 w-12 text-muted-foreground mb-4" />
    <p className="text-lg font-semibold">No items yet</p>
    <p className="text-sm text-muted-foreground mt-2">Get started by creating one.</p>
    <Button className="mt-4">Create Item</Button>
  </div>
  ```

  ## Loading Patterns
  ```tsx
  // Skeleton
  <Skeleton className="h-4 w-[200px]" />
  
  // Button loading
  <Button disabled>
    <Loader2Icon className="mr-2 h-4 w-4 animate-spin" />
    Saving...
  </Button>
  ```

  ## Icon Sizes
  - In buttons: `h-4 w-4` with `mr-2` spacing
  - Standalone: `h-5 w-5 text-muted-foreground`
  - Large/empty state: `h-12 w-12`

  ## Common Classes Reference
  - Focus ring: `focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-1 focus-visible:ring-ring`
  - Disabled: `disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:opacity-50`
  - Muted text: `text-muted-foreground`
  - Card surface: `bg-card text-card-foreground`
  - Glassmorphism: `bg-gradient-to-b from-white/10 to-white/5 backdrop-blur-xl border border-white/10`

  ## Do's
  - Import components from `@/components/ui/*`
  - Use semantic color classes (bg-primary, text-muted-foreground)
  - Use `cn()` for conditional class merging
  - Follow established component patterns
  - Use space-y-* or gap-* for consistent spacing

  ## Don'ts
  - Don't use arbitrary color values—use CSS variables
  - Don't create new components when existing ones work
  - Don't use inline styles
  - Don't skip loading and error states
  - Don't forget accessibility (labels, aria attributes)
}
